59.6	Mark_Steyn	Mark Steyn	Mark Steyn (born December 8, 1959) is a Canadian-born writer, conservative-leaning political commentator, and cultural critic. He has written five books, including America Alone: The End of the World As We Know It, a New York Times bestseller. He is published in newspapers and magazines, appears on shows such as those of Rush Limbaugh, Hugh Hewitt, and Sean Hannity.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8a/Mark_Steyn.jpg/220px-Mark_Steyn.jpg
